A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Chapter 1 of Title 50 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to
2 general provisions regarding state government, so as to prohibit state agencies and local
3 government entities from responding to ransomware activity; to require that state agencies
4 and local government entities report ransomware activity to the Georgia Technology
5 Authority; to provide for definitions; to provide for related matters; to repeal conflicting
6 laws; and for other purposes.
7 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
8 SECTION 1.
9 Chapter 1 of Title 50 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to general
10 provisions regarding state government, is amended by adding a new Code section to read as
11 follows:
12 "50-1-14.
13 (a) As used in this Code section, the term:
14 (1) 'Local government entity' means any political subdivision of this state, including any
15 county, consolidated government, municipality, authority, school district, commission,
